1
00:00:01,039 --> 00:00:02,039
Wait.

2
00:00:02,039 --> 00:00:03,239
(Episode 57)

3
00:00:06,249 --> 00:00:09,049
I'm Park Min Jun.

4
00:00:10,119 --> 00:00:12,589
Next time we meet,

5
00:00:12,989 --> 00:00:15,419
just call me by my name, Chloe.

6
00:00:19,389 --> 00:00:20,399
Right.

7
00:00:38,409 --> 00:00:39,509
Min Jun.

8
00:00:42,019 --> 00:00:44,319
I was holding up so well,

9
00:00:45,319 --> 00:00:46,919
acting as if I'd forgotten you too.

10
00:00:48,159 --> 00:00:50,829
But in the end, when you called me Chloe,

11
00:00:51,529 --> 00:00:53,829
that one word made me crumble.

12
00:01:05,669 --> 00:01:09,379
I was terrified my revenge would make me lose you.

13
00:01:10,179 --> 00:01:11,509
I really was.

14
00:01:12,179 --> 00:01:15,819
Over and over, I regretted not listening to you.

15
00:01:26,429 --> 00:01:28,399
For making it out alive,

16
00:01:29,359 --> 00:01:30,369
and for...

17
00:01:31,599 --> 00:01:32,669
forgetting me...

18
00:01:33,639 --> 00:01:34,839
I'm so, so grateful.

19
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:39,269
You just go on and be happy again.

20
00:01:40,639 --> 00:01:43,209
And me... I'll just...

21
00:01:49,949 --> 00:01:50,949
What?

22
00:01:53,089 --> 00:01:55,619
You're actually crying?

23
00:01:58,989 --> 00:02:02,659
Wait, what's wrong? Did I say something wrong?

24
00:02:05,599 --> 00:02:07,799
No, it's not you...

25
00:02:12,969 --> 00:02:16,209
This has nothing to do with you, Park Min Jun.

26
00:02:19,149 --> 00:02:20,249
I mean...

27
00:02:29,889 --> 00:02:30,889
Hyun...

28
00:02:35,699 --> 00:02:36,699
Alright, then.

29
00:02:37,469 --> 00:02:39,999
If you don't want to talk about it, that's fine.

30
00:02:44,509 --> 00:02:45,709
Get some rest.

31
00:02:49,909 --> 00:02:51,149
Our Hyun Jun...

32
00:02:52,549 --> 00:02:56,379
Is he really going to leave for the US?

33
00:03:06,229 --> 00:03:07,229
Our...

34
00:03:08,429 --> 00:03:09,529
"Our Hyun Jun?"

35
00:03:15,139 --> 00:03:17,409
Is it because of Oh Jung Ran and Mr. Song's relationship...

36
00:03:18,169 --> 00:03:19,839
that I'm overthinking this?

37
00:03:21,839 --> 00:03:23,079
Still, something feels off.

38
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:34,319
Sir.

39
00:03:36,819 --> 00:03:38,129
Honestly, about Jin Ju...

40
00:03:40,299 --> 00:03:42,959
It's a blessing in disguise that she lost her memory.

41
00:03:43,769 --> 00:03:45,999
The last seven years were hard on her, weren't they?

42
00:03:48,339 --> 00:03:49,899
Forgetting everything like this...

43
00:03:52,669 --> 00:03:55,109
and starting over wouldn't be bad, would it?

44
00:03:57,809 --> 00:03:59,709
You feel the same way, don't you, sir?

45
00:04:06,249 --> 00:04:09,119
Their relationship was impossible to begin with.

46
00:04:11,129 --> 00:04:12,859
For their story to end like this...

47
00:04:14,329 --> 00:04:16,399
It's for the best, don't you think?

48
00:04:20,169 --> 00:04:21,239
I miss you.

49
00:04:26,539 --> 00:04:27,839
(Park Min Jun)

50
00:04:39,019 --> 00:04:40,019
Right.

51
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:43,629
The best thing is to wrap things up and go back to the US.

52
00:04:44,329 --> 00:04:46,189
I don't want to go back.

53
00:04:50,259 --> 00:04:51,269
You scared me.

54
00:04:52,199 --> 00:04:53,399
How did you get here?

55
00:04:53,769 --> 00:04:57,009
You said you don't remember a thing. Did you remember this place?

56
00:05:01,739 --> 00:05:03,539
You can get rid of these,

57
00:05:06,809 --> 00:05:08,749
but I can't leave for the US.

58
00:05:09,649 --> 00:05:10,749
Because...

59
00:05:11,689 --> 00:05:13,189
I'm Baek Jin Ju, after all.

60
00:05:14,859 --> 00:05:15,859
What?

61
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:17,959
You...

62
00:05:18,389 --> 00:05:21,359
There were too many eyes on me at the hospital.

63
00:05:21,859 --> 00:05:25,069
I figured Chairman Park had people spying on me,

64
00:05:26,269 --> 00:05:29,699
I had to fool you too, James. I'm sorry.

65
00:05:32,769 --> 00:05:33,939
Jin Ju...

66
00:05:34,509 --> 00:05:35,679
You little...

67
00:05:36,039 --> 00:05:37,409
James.

68
00:05:39,949 --> 00:05:41,819
My plan for revenge...

69
00:05:44,349 --> 00:05:46,319
was a miserable failure.

70
00:05:49,859 --> 00:05:51,559
My plan to have Choi Yu Na...

71
00:05:51,859 --> 00:05:54,729
kill Park Tae Ho must have been a mistake.

72
00:05:56,429 --> 00:05:58,629
That's why Min Jun almost died,

73
00:05:59,929 --> 00:06:01,139
and even lost his memory...

74
00:06:02,139 --> 00:06:03,569
I...

75
00:06:04,139 --> 00:06:05,969
I ruined everything.

76
00:06:07,779 --> 00:06:09,139
Jin Ju.

77
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:10,879
I'm...

78
00:06:11,279 --> 00:06:13,679
just so furious and this is so unfair!

79
00:06:13,979 --> 00:06:16,219
I can't just give up like this.

80
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:19,289
For my dad's sake,

81
00:06:19,589 --> 00:06:22,989
I desperately want Park Tae Ho and Choi Yu Na to pay!

82
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:25,589
I want to start over!

83
00:06:29,229 --> 00:06:30,799
But now, the only way...

84
00:06:33,469 --> 00:06:35,699
is to let Min Jun go.

85
00:06:38,339 --> 00:06:41,509
Leaving Min Jun behind when he doesn't even remember me...

86
00:06:42,609 --> 00:06:46,049
I just have no choice but to go on alone.

87
00:06:48,549 --> 00:06:50,689
Leaving Min Jun behind.

88
00:06:51,719 --> 00:06:53,249
I feel so guilty,

89
00:06:54,759 --> 00:06:55,889
and it hurts so much.

90
00:06:58,929 --> 00:07:03,329
But I couldn't say a single word to him.

91
00:07:04,699 --> 00:07:08,899
I couldn't thank him or tell him I was sorry.

92
00:07:09,999 --> 00:07:12,569
I couldn't say anything at all.

93
00:07:16,709 --> 00:07:19,409
I know. It's okay, Jin Ju.

94
00:07:30,059 --> 00:07:32,029
All this regret and pain...

95
00:07:33,089 --> 00:07:34,829
I'm done with it after today.

96
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:41,169
Starting tomorrow, I'll go back to fooling Park Tae Ho, Choi Yu Na,

97
00:07:42,239 --> 00:07:43,599
And I will...

98
00:07:44,139 --> 00:07:46,569
start my revenge all over again.

99
00:07:49,409 --> 00:07:51,649
Jin Ju...

100
00:07:54,179 --> 00:07:56,079
(Adele)

101
00:07:56,149 --> 00:07:57,249
(Kim Myung Hui)

102
00:07:59,119 --> 00:08:00,919
Mr. Song and Hyun Jun.

103
00:08:01,659 --> 00:08:03,019
Am I just overthinking this?

104
00:08:03,489 --> 00:08:06,529
Mr. Song has a thing for Oh Jung Ran,

105
00:08:06,629 --> 00:08:09,759
So wouldn't he have a soft spot for her son, Park Hyun Jun?

106
00:08:14,799 --> 00:08:18,839
If Mr. Song is his real father, that's a huge bombshell.

107
00:08:19,409 --> 00:08:21,609
If we play our cards right, it's a huge win,

108
00:08:21,979 --> 00:08:25,009
but if we mishandle it, it could blow up in our faces.

109
00:08:26,349 --> 00:08:28,679
Do some more digging on Mr. Song.

110
00:08:29,119 --> 00:08:32,249
Okay. I already looked into his past,

111
00:08:32,389 --> 00:08:34,819
so I guess I should look for a link to Park Hyun Jun now.

112
00:08:35,789 --> 00:08:39,189
He's in his car a lot, so I'll start with that first.

113
00:08:44,229 --> 00:08:46,469
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

114
00:08:50,869 --> 00:08:53,339
The money for Assemblyman Kwon is ready.

115
00:08:53,469 --> 00:08:57,379
We'll wire it from the Swiss account to his secret account.

116
00:09:02,719 --> 00:09:05,389
Good. Set a meeting with Assemblyman Kwon.

117
00:09:06,219 --> 00:09:09,559
The development rights, crucial to Adele Group's future and power...

118
00:09:10,359 --> 00:09:12,829
are finally within reach.

119
00:09:14,129 --> 00:09:16,699
This whole deal, from start to finish,

120
00:09:17,059 --> 00:09:18,699
I'm the one who made it happen.

121
00:09:20,699 --> 00:09:21,699
So?

122
00:09:22,099 --> 00:09:24,909
From running the gallery to handling secret deals.

123
00:09:25,469 --> 00:09:29,579
Remember, things run perfectly fine, even without Jung Ran.

124
00:09:31,149 --> 00:09:34,719
Are you really trying to take Oh Jung Ran's place?

125
00:09:34,849 --> 00:09:36,979
You never know what might happen.

126
00:09:37,819 --> 00:09:41,189
If, by some chance, Jung Ran were to make a grave mistake,

127
00:09:41,259 --> 00:09:46,229
I'm just letting you know I'm ready to take her place in any capacity.

128
00:09:47,059 --> 00:09:48,459
I see.

129
00:09:49,459 --> 00:09:50,499
I'll keep that in mind.

130
00:10:04,309 --> 00:10:08,479
The way you're dressed right now doesn't really feel like you.

131
00:10:09,649 --> 00:10:12,049
It looks like you're wearing...

132
00:10:12,719 --> 00:10:14,589
someone else's clothes.

133
00:10:23,529 --> 00:10:25,029
So what if I did?

134
00:10:26,169 --> 00:10:29,439
I don't care, as long as I can win Min Jun's heart.

135
00:10:31,139 --> 00:10:32,139
But...

136
00:10:32,469 --> 00:10:35,309
Why does Park Min Jun keep showing so much interest in Chloe?

137
00:10:36,409 --> 00:10:39,479
What if his memories come back because of her?

138
00:10:47,589 --> 00:10:50,459
Your cards and bank accounts have all been frozen.

139
00:10:50,519 --> 00:10:53,689
Fine. Tell them to do whatever they want.

140
00:10:54,459 --> 00:10:55,799
It's actually liberating.

141
00:11:12,509 --> 00:11:14,449
I'm not in the mood to deal with you...

142
00:11:14,449 --> 00:11:16,379
so just go find your Min Jun.

143
00:11:16,449 --> 00:11:19,049
I was going to see Min Jun anyway and just stopped by.

144
00:11:19,819 --> 00:11:22,419
- To give you some advice. - Advice?

145
00:11:22,489 --> 00:11:26,059
This plan to marry Chloe and go to the US.

146
00:11:26,259 --> 00:11:28,529
Shouldn't you switch the order and hurry it up?

147
00:11:29,159 --> 00:11:32,899
Just take Chloe to the US, and you can get married there.

148
00:11:33,199 --> 00:11:37,039
Stop making excuses and just go already.

149
00:11:37,139 --> 00:11:38,139
What?

150
00:11:39,339 --> 00:11:42,009
It seems like Chairman took everything.

151
00:11:42,009 --> 00:11:44,009
He clearly won't approve.

152
00:11:44,179 --> 00:11:46,679
Your mother was against Chloe from the start, too.

153
00:11:51,389 --> 00:11:54,019
Wow, you must be really nervous.

154
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:55,519
Why's that?

155
00:11:55,989 --> 00:11:58,089
You went so far as to imitate Baek Jin Ju,

156
00:11:58,629 --> 00:12:00,129
and you still can't win over Park Min Jun?

157
00:12:00,629 --> 00:12:03,399
So what's going on between Park Min Jun and Chloe...

158
00:12:03,699 --> 00:12:04,829
is really getting to you?

159
00:12:05,769 --> 00:12:08,639
You're right. Park Min Jun and Chloe.

160
00:12:08,699 --> 00:12:12,969
They met again, even without their memories.

161
00:12:13,809 --> 00:12:16,909
If their memories return, am I the only one who loses?

162
00:12:17,109 --> 00:12:19,779
You have no idea what will happen with Chloe either.

163
00:12:29,489 --> 00:12:32,989
Your anxiety is your problem.

164
00:12:33,629 --> 00:12:37,259
I'll handle my own business with Chloe.

165
00:12:55,319 --> 00:12:56,449
I'm...

166
00:12:57,319 --> 00:12:58,819
still furious.

167
00:12:59,519 --> 00:13:01,219
I can't believe Park Tae Ho and Choi Yu Na...

168
00:13:01,719 --> 00:13:03,959
set a trap to try and kill you.

169
00:13:05,859 --> 00:13:08,259
With no guilt over the past, they tried to kill again?

170
00:13:11,229 --> 00:13:12,869
I was so furious...

171
00:13:13,429 --> 00:13:14,899
I couldn't sleep a wink.

172
00:13:16,299 --> 00:13:18,769
If it hadn't been for Park Min Jun, you really could have died.

173
00:13:19,139 --> 00:13:20,139
Yes.

174
00:13:20,709 --> 00:13:22,579
Min Jun is the one who saved me.

175
00:13:23,009 --> 00:13:24,009
Right.

176
00:13:24,509 --> 00:13:25,509
But...

177
00:13:26,049 --> 00:13:27,619
what happened with the car accident?

178
00:13:28,049 --> 00:13:30,849
Chairman Park was also determined to get to the bottom of it.

179
00:13:30,989 --> 00:13:34,359
Yes, I don't think Chairman Park was the one targeting me.

180
00:13:34,619 --> 00:13:37,789
Then if it wasn't just a random hit-and-run,

181
00:13:38,629 --> 00:13:41,159
then it's highly likely they were after Park Min Jun, right?

182
00:13:41,699 --> 00:13:43,159
I was thinking the same thing.

183
00:13:43,859 --> 00:13:46,369
If Min Jun was the target, then it was probably...

184
00:13:47,369 --> 00:13:48,369
Oh Jung Ran.

185
00:13:49,869 --> 00:13:51,369
She must be behind it.

186
00:13:54,309 --> 00:13:56,639
She has killed before, after all.

187
00:14:01,719 --> 00:14:04,889
And you're still determined to get revenge?

188
00:14:05,589 --> 00:14:07,149
Even though you almost died,

189
00:14:07,489 --> 00:14:09,519
and it could get even more dangerous for you.

190
00:14:09,689 --> 00:14:11,089
If I run away now,

191
00:14:11,589 --> 00:14:13,859
that means I'd be letting Park Tae Ho and Choi Yu Na win.

192
00:14:14,429 --> 00:14:18,229
My dad's name would never be cleared,

193
00:14:18,899 --> 00:14:22,539
and I'd fall apart, blaming myself and living in guilt.

194
00:14:23,369 --> 00:14:24,809
No matter how dangerous it gets,

195
00:14:25,639 --> 00:14:27,909
until I can take those two down,

196
00:14:28,439 --> 00:14:30,309
I can never give up.

197
00:14:33,279 --> 00:14:34,819
Gosh, Jin Ju, you're really something.

198
00:14:37,749 --> 00:14:38,749
So...

199
00:14:39,719 --> 00:14:41,559
do you have a next step planned?

200
00:14:46,529 --> 00:14:48,459
(Director Park Hyun Jun)

201
00:14:50,859 --> 00:14:51,929
First,

202
00:14:52,729 --> 00:14:55,539
I need to find a way to get into Adele.

203
00:15:05,979 --> 00:15:10,319
Hey, Na Yeon. Good work today. Your shift's over. Head home.

204
00:15:10,619 --> 00:15:13,619
- But it's so busy right now. - Come on, a deal's a deal.

205
00:15:13,689 --> 00:15:16,719
Then let's make a new deal.

206
00:15:17,389 --> 00:15:20,759
- I'll work overtime for double pay. - Double?

207
00:15:22,159 --> 00:15:24,469
- That's a little... - Just do it.

208
00:15:24,769 --> 00:15:28,199
If I break something, I can say, "Just take it out of my check."

209
00:15:32,039 --> 00:15:34,409
Welcome back. It's been a while.

210
00:15:35,179 --> 00:15:38,149
I heard about the accident. How are you feeling? Are you okay?

211
00:15:40,109 --> 00:15:43,949
Right. Maybe you don't remember me. You were a regular here.

212
00:15:44,819 --> 00:15:48,159
Please sit down. Would you like coffee, a meal, or dessert?

213
00:15:50,859 --> 00:15:52,189
You're here already.

214
00:15:53,459 --> 00:15:54,529
But...

215
00:15:55,499 --> 00:15:56,799
maybe we should go talk somewhere else?

216
00:15:56,859 --> 00:15:59,699
Oh? Why? Is there a problem with my cafe?

217
00:16:00,929 --> 00:16:02,999
No, it's not that...

218
00:16:08,839 --> 00:16:10,009
Enjoy your food.

219
00:16:12,279 --> 00:16:13,749
I should have treated you.

220
00:16:14,419 --> 00:16:15,619
I must look like a mess.

221
00:16:16,479 --> 00:16:17,789
Does it matter who pays?

222
00:16:18,789 --> 00:16:23,659
Chairman is so against this he cut off your cards?

223
00:16:23,819 --> 00:16:25,959
Don't worry too much about it.

224
00:16:26,589 --> 00:16:29,399
One credit card wasn't going to change my mind.

225
00:16:31,969 --> 00:16:33,499
If anything, it made my decision easier.

226
00:16:34,099 --> 00:16:35,269
Your decision?

227
00:16:36,569 --> 00:16:37,839
When are you leaving for the US?

228
00:16:39,569 --> 00:16:40,839
I'm going with you.

229
00:16:42,979 --> 00:16:43,979
What?

230
00:16:44,039 --> 00:16:48,079
Your father leaves for the US soon. I'll work around his schedule.

231
00:16:48,149 --> 00:16:51,249
I don't mind getting married in the US.

232
00:16:53,889 --> 00:16:57,259
Are you serious about coming with me?

233
00:16:58,889 --> 00:17:01,259
But you need to become Adele Group's heir.

234
00:17:02,029 --> 00:17:05,399
If you come with me, you'll give up your position as heir.

235
00:17:06,129 --> 00:17:10,699
And you might even be cut off from your family.

236
00:17:11,839 --> 00:17:13,409
Adele Group's heir...

237
00:17:14,539 --> 00:17:16,179
I was never interested to begin with.

238
00:17:16,879 --> 00:17:19,749
And I've already told my family that I'm leaving.

239
00:17:19,849 --> 00:17:23,449
You might regret giving all this up.

240
00:17:24,219 --> 00:17:26,519
My only regret...

241
00:17:27,549 --> 00:17:29,359
would be losing you.

242
00:17:31,529 --> 00:17:33,429
Let's leave together...

243
00:17:34,999 --> 00:17:36,229
and start fresh.

244
00:17:40,529 --> 00:17:43,899
Then you'll have to meet my dad.

245
00:17:45,369 --> 00:17:48,409
I'll set up a time and get back to you.

246
00:18:02,389 --> 00:18:04,219
Get rid of Butler Ok. Now.

247
00:18:04,759 --> 00:18:08,099
I can't stand her, so fire her and find a replacement.

248
00:18:08,999 --> 00:18:12,329
Last time, you wanted me to erase all traces of Min Jun.

249
00:18:12,699 --> 00:18:15,039
And now you're nitpicking about Butler Ok?

250
00:18:15,539 --> 00:18:19,469
Your son is one thing, but can't you fire the butler?

251
00:18:19,609 --> 00:18:21,139
It's hard to find someone...

252
00:18:21,209 --> 00:18:24,809
as discreet as Butler Ok. You know that.

253
00:18:24,909 --> 00:18:28,979
For over ten years, none of our secrets has gotten out.

254
00:18:29,179 --> 00:18:31,889
So it's no on Park Min Jun, and no on Butler Ok.

255
00:18:32,689 --> 00:18:34,459
Then what about Chloe?

256
00:18:38,059 --> 00:18:42,459
I can't change Hyun Jun's mind. But I can't let him go to the US.

257
00:18:42,559 --> 00:18:44,259
To get him to stay,

258
00:18:44,869 --> 00:18:46,699
that Chloe thing has to disappear.

259
00:18:47,529 --> 00:18:50,439
You were getting rid of her anyway. Why not just do it again?

260
00:19:03,749 --> 00:19:05,989
What is this about...

261
00:19:06,649 --> 00:19:10,019
- without making an appointment? - I need to confirm something.

262
00:19:10,089 --> 00:19:11,129
Is that right?

263
00:19:13,129 --> 00:19:16,459
Perfect. There was something I wanted to confirm with you, too.

264
00:19:16,899 --> 00:19:21,369
You survived a crash, got amnesia, and yet you have the nerve...

265
00:19:21,439 --> 00:19:23,439
to cling to my Hyun Jun?

266
00:19:23,639 --> 00:19:27,469
So you must be Hyun Jun's mother.

267
00:19:28,839 --> 00:19:32,049
But ma'am, I think you're mistaken.

268
00:19:33,079 --> 00:19:37,349
It's not me clinging to him. He's the one clinging to me.

269
00:19:38,489 --> 00:19:41,959
In fact, he said he's coming with me to the US.

270
00:19:43,059 --> 00:19:45,889
That's only because you led him on!

271
00:19:46,359 --> 00:19:49,429
My Hyun Jun is meant to own Adele Group!

272
00:19:49,529 --> 00:19:52,429
He's my life and everything. The US? Out of the question.

273
00:19:53,329 --> 00:19:56,399
I'd sooner die than let him go.

274
00:19:57,099 --> 00:19:58,239
I see.

275
00:19:59,409 --> 00:20:02,679
Your life and everything.

276
00:20:04,009 --> 00:20:05,509
And what about you, Chairman?

277
00:20:06,079 --> 00:20:10,379
Is Hyun Jun your life and your everything, too?

278
00:20:12,619 --> 00:20:16,659
Hyun Jun has to live for Adele Group.

279
00:20:16,759 --> 00:20:19,059
As Park Tae Ho's son,

280
00:20:19,829 --> 00:20:22,099
he must serve his purpose.

281
00:20:23,329 --> 00:20:27,799
He can't leave for the US with you, nor can he marry you, Ms. Chloe.

282
00:20:28,639 --> 00:20:31,199
It would be best for you to leave on your own...

283
00:20:31,909 --> 00:20:33,069
While I'm giving you the chance.

284
00:20:34,809 --> 00:20:39,679
So, to you, Chairman, Adele Group is more important than your own son.

285
00:20:40,449 --> 00:20:43,679
I understand you both perfectly.

286
00:20:44,049 --> 00:20:45,549
I'll wrap things up on my end quickly.

287
00:20:57,299 --> 00:20:59,199
His life and everything?

288
00:21:00,469 --> 00:21:01,869
More like their greed.

289
00:21:05,269 --> 00:21:07,569
Jung Ran just wants Park Hyun Jun,

290
00:21:08,079 --> 00:21:10,109
and Park Tae Ho just wants the Adele Group.

291
00:21:13,849 --> 00:21:17,049
I see exactly what you both truly desire.

292
00:21:22,919 --> 00:21:27,589
Nothing's going my way. I can't get rid of Butler Ok or Chloe.

293
00:21:27,789 --> 00:21:30,129
Wait, you were going to do something to Chloe too?

294
00:21:31,029 --> 00:21:34,369
Is that what you went and asked Chairman Park to do?

295
00:21:34,429 --> 00:21:37,369
Hyun Jun is about to give it all up and leave. Should I just watch?

296
00:21:37,539 --> 00:21:40,069
I can't exactly tie him up and keep him here, can I?

297
00:21:40,139 --> 00:21:41,939
So I had to at least get rid of Chloe.

298
00:21:42,009 --> 00:21:45,709
This will blow up in your face if Hyun Jun finds out.

299
00:21:46,479 --> 00:21:51,249
Please, I'm begging you. Just let Hyun Jun go.

300
00:21:51,849 --> 00:21:56,059
Don't be ridiculous. I will never let my Hyun Jun go to the US.

301
00:21:56,319 --> 00:21:59,359
I'll stop Chloe and the plane myself if I have to...

302
00:22:00,959 --> 00:22:01,959
Wait a second.

303
00:22:03,029 --> 00:22:05,469
Stopping him from boarding the plane comes first, right?

304
00:22:06,499 --> 00:22:09,999
His passport. I should hide Hyun Jun's passport.

305
00:22:10,599 --> 00:22:11,609
Wait, but...

306
00:22:21,419 --> 00:22:24,989
I can't even tell her President Kim is blackmailing me.

307
00:22:26,149 --> 00:22:31,059
What will I do if she keeps having these dangerous thoughts?

308
00:22:34,259 --> 00:22:36,959
I'm afraid I'll just give President Kim the evidence myself...

309
00:22:37,929 --> 00:22:41,329
and want Jung Ran to get a divorce. I'm serious...

310
00:22:44,099 --> 00:22:46,569
I feel like I'm going to lose my mind.

311
00:23:01,319 --> 00:23:06,289
Park Hyun Jun, you sure keep interesting things.

312
00:23:07,729 --> 00:23:09,899
I wish you could talk.

313
00:23:10,059 --> 00:23:13,129
You wouldn't lie or hide anything from me.

314
00:23:13,529 --> 00:23:15,539
You would have told me everything about...

315
00:23:15,969 --> 00:23:17,969
everything about the memories I lost.

316
00:23:21,269 --> 00:23:22,279
What do you think you're doing?

317
00:23:22,709 --> 00:23:24,909
Why are you sitting in my Hyun Jun's chair?

318
00:23:25,509 --> 00:23:26,509
I just...

319
00:23:27,279 --> 00:23:31,949
Then again, you've always been after my Hyun Jun's position.

320
00:23:33,149 --> 00:23:37,289
Have you always been like this? I mean, before I lost my memories,

321
00:23:37,789 --> 00:23:39,789
were you always this way with me?

322
00:23:39,859 --> 00:23:43,329
Do you think we were all smiles and laughter?

323
00:23:44,059 --> 00:23:47,229
Not when you and your mother kept eyeing our place.

324
00:23:48,339 --> 00:23:50,539
In fact, you should be the one to leave for the US.

325
00:23:50,939 --> 00:23:53,409
Just take that Chloe girl and get out of here now!

326
00:23:54,369 --> 00:23:55,379
Chloe?

327
00:23:56,539 --> 00:23:58,409
- The one from the accident with... - Ma'am.

328
00:23:59,609 --> 00:24:02,049
You can't say things that will upset Min Jun.

329
00:24:02,449 --> 00:24:04,679
If he gets those headaches again and starts to struggle,

330
00:24:05,389 --> 00:24:08,159
it won't just be President Kim, Chairman will be furious.

331
00:24:20,869 --> 00:24:24,069
What was that all about? Why did she say to leave with Chloe?

332
00:24:25,369 --> 00:24:28,209
You know she's against Park Hyun Jun and Chloe getting married.

333
00:24:28,639 --> 00:24:32,049
She can't stand Chloe, so she's just lashing out.

334
00:24:33,579 --> 00:24:36,079
You know what she's like.

335
00:24:36,319 --> 00:24:38,119
I'm asking you because I know what she's like.

336
00:24:38,949 --> 00:24:42,059
She wasn't just making things up. She said it with genuine malice.

337
00:24:42,289 --> 00:24:44,489
At least the part about Chloe had to be true.

338
00:24:45,659 --> 00:24:46,659
Yu Na.

339
00:24:46,989 --> 00:24:49,799
Stop hiding things and just be honest with me.

340
00:24:52,329 --> 00:24:54,729
- Choi Yu Na. - I did tell you the truth.

341
00:24:55,339 --> 00:24:57,899
If you don't believe me, go ask your mother.

342
00:24:59,869 --> 00:25:00,909
You said it yourself,

343
00:25:01,169 --> 00:25:03,239
that you can trust whatever your mother says.

344
00:25:04,909 --> 00:25:07,449
Anything more I say will make you more suspicious,

345
00:25:08,819 --> 00:25:10,249
so just ask your mother.

346
00:25:17,859 --> 00:25:19,459
A simple slip of the tongue?

347
00:25:20,489 --> 00:25:21,489
No.

348
00:25:22,129 --> 00:25:23,799
At least, when it comes to Chloe and me,

349
00:25:24,429 --> 00:25:26,199
there's definitely something there.

350
00:25:37,839 --> 00:25:39,449
Please, be more careful.

351
00:25:39,779 --> 00:25:42,079
Stop saying such strange things in front of Min Jun.

352
00:25:44,619 --> 00:25:46,649
Who do you think you are, lecturing me?

353
00:25:47,719 --> 00:25:50,459
That's rich, coming from someone lying to a man with amnesia.

354
00:25:50,559 --> 00:25:52,859
It's necessary for Min Jun's recovery.

355
00:25:53,459 --> 00:25:56,559
President Kim and Chairman gave me permission.

356
00:25:57,799 --> 00:26:00,299
Don't you ever talk about Chloe in front of Min Jun again.

357
00:26:00,799 --> 00:26:03,799
That nonsense about their accident, or both losing their memories...

358
00:26:04,299 --> 00:26:07,909
If that garbage makes him remember, it will ruin all my work...

359
00:26:13,249 --> 00:26:15,019
Whatever you're planning,

360
00:26:15,849 --> 00:26:17,579
I'll ruin it all.

361
00:26:25,059 --> 00:26:27,129
If Park Min Jun gets his memory back?

362
00:26:28,559 --> 00:26:31,429
If he remembers and starts talking about the day of the accident...

363
00:26:32,399 --> 00:26:35,099
Right, that wouldn't be good for me either.

364
00:26:37,099 --> 00:26:38,639
Great. Now I have to watch my mouth too?

365
00:26:39,639 --> 00:26:42,039
How did I end up backed into a corner like this?

366
00:26:43,979 --> 00:26:44,979
This won't do.

367
00:26:45,449 --> 00:26:48,849
I need to get a grip and handle them one by one.

368
00:26:50,479 --> 00:26:53,089
So, who do I deal with first?

369
00:27:06,599 --> 00:27:07,969
(Vehicle Registration)

370
00:27:17,009 --> 00:27:18,379
Is this it?

371
00:27:30,319 --> 00:27:31,929
I've taken care of the CCTV.

372
00:27:31,989 --> 00:27:34,389
And I erased the dashcam footage.

373
00:27:34,689 --> 00:27:38,429
- Find anything in the car? - Nothing special.

374
00:27:38,729 --> 00:27:41,939
Just Mr. Song's wallet. Look.

375
00:27:45,839 --> 00:27:47,269
It's a picture of a little kid.

376
00:27:50,609 --> 00:27:52,879
Wait a minute. This child is...

377
00:27:55,119 --> 00:27:58,119
That's right. It's Hyun Jun when he was little.

378
00:27:59,919 --> 00:28:03,019
Then Mr. Song really is...

379
00:28:07,689 --> 00:28:08,699
Oh my.

380
00:28:19,039 --> 00:28:20,669
Sir, what is this place?

381
00:28:21,439 --> 00:28:22,479
Go on inside.

382
00:28:34,689 --> 00:28:37,759
(The late Baek Jun Gi, The late Baek Jin Ju)

383
00:28:43,899 --> 00:28:45,869
What is going on here?

384
00:28:46,629 --> 00:28:48,129
Pay your respects to my dad.

385
00:28:49,839 --> 00:28:50,839
You...

386
00:28:52,069 --> 00:28:53,669
You didn't really lose your memory?

387
00:28:56,509 --> 00:28:57,509
So you did know.

388
00:28:59,109 --> 00:29:00,679
You knew who I really was.

389
00:29:03,019 --> 00:29:04,019
Was it when...

390
00:29:05,089 --> 00:29:07,589
you fed me that chestnut cake?

391
00:29:08,759 --> 00:29:10,689
You wanted to be Chloe until the very end.

392
00:29:12,689 --> 00:29:15,759
So I did everything I could to treat you as Chloe. Why?

393
00:29:17,029 --> 00:29:18,429
Why are you suddenly acting like this?

394
00:29:20,569 --> 00:29:21,569
The reason...

395
00:29:26,109 --> 00:29:27,909
Where do I even begin to explain?

396
00:29:40,289 --> 00:29:44,089
This is going to be a very painful story.

397
00:29:45,529 --> 00:29:47,959
But don't turn away. I need you to listen to the end.

398
00:29:48,829 --> 00:29:52,029
Because it's something you have to know.

399
00:29:57,269 --> 00:29:59,239
Oh my. What?

400
00:30:02,479 --> 00:30:04,409
That's weird.

401
00:30:04,909 --> 00:30:07,249
Where did my wallet go?

402
00:30:08,649 --> 00:30:09,919
Wait, what is this?

403
00:30:15,659 --> 00:30:17,119
Hey! What do you think you're doing?

404
00:30:17,959 --> 00:30:19,859
I think you might've dropped this.

405
00:30:23,759 --> 00:30:25,029
You could have just said something.

406
00:30:25,769 --> 00:30:28,499
I'm the type to act first and talk later.

407
00:30:33,609 --> 00:30:34,809
Seriously?

408
00:30:54,089 --> 00:30:56,899
Seven years ago, my father did that to your father...

409
00:30:58,399 --> 00:31:00,999
And when you came back, you went after my father...

410
00:31:02,399 --> 00:31:03,569
And then my father...

411
00:31:06,339 --> 00:31:07,339
tried to kill you?

412
00:31:08,639 --> 00:31:10,479
A cycle of everyone trying to kill each other.

413
00:31:10,909 --> 00:31:11,909
That...

414
00:31:13,509 --> 00:31:15,279
is what you turned your back on and ran from.

415
00:31:17,179 --> 00:31:18,279
The truth.

416
00:31:26,629 --> 00:31:28,529
When you figured out who I really was,

417
00:31:29,859 --> 00:31:32,999
when Min Jun left home over the Temi Bio issue, you...

418
00:31:34,269 --> 00:31:36,839
always chose to look away at the very last moment.

419
00:31:38,339 --> 00:31:40,139
The truth you would have had to face...

420
00:31:41,569 --> 00:31:42,779
must have been terrifying.

421
00:31:45,039 --> 00:31:48,009
Are you going to run away and hide this time too?

422
00:31:49,779 --> 00:31:51,649
In the face of your father's evil,

423
00:31:52,119 --> 00:31:54,649
before my father, who was sacrificed unjustly,

424
00:31:55,489 --> 00:31:58,559
will you run away as murderer Park Tae Ho's son?

425
00:31:59,189 --> 00:32:01,489
So what do you want me to do about it?

426
00:32:02,599 --> 00:32:04,959
Help me become part of the Adele family.

427
00:32:06,769 --> 00:32:07,869
Open the door for me.

428
00:32:08,639 --> 00:32:09,639
I...

429
00:32:12,509 --> 00:32:14,669
I need to become the owner of Adele.

430
00:32:42,369 --> 00:32:45,409
(Pearl in Red)

431
00:32:45,469 --> 00:32:47,069
Park Min Jun and Park Hyun Jun...

432
00:32:47,309 --> 00:32:50,579
It must be a heavy burden, being the sons of Park Tae Ho.

433
00:32:50,809 --> 00:32:55,619
I came before Baek Jin Ju. I loved him first and waited...

434
00:32:55,749 --> 00:32:58,949
Don't I deserve to win his heart, just for once?

435
00:32:59,349 --> 00:33:01,649
I'll turn in the evidence and have her thrown out.

436
00:33:01,889 --> 00:33:04,559
Whatever it takes to follow Hyun Jun to the US...

437
00:33:05,429 --> 00:33:08,459
How could you, of all people, do this to me?
